## Development

```bash
# Run tests
poetry run pytest

# Run with coverage
poetry run pytest --cov=src

# Run the CLI during development
poetry run simplepydoc generate --repo ./src/llm_docgen --output ./docs

# Format code
poetry run black src tests

# Lint
poetry run flake8 src tests
```

